==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Long-sighted
<hw>Long"-sight`ed</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>Able to see objects at a great distance; hence, having great
foresight; sagacious; farseeing.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Able to see objects distinctly at a distance, but
not close at hand; hypermetropic.</def><-- = farsighted, hyperopic?
-->⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Long-sightedness</ent>⟦br⟧
